class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，依，唔係波，樓價好似唔識跌仲升緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一定架喇，呢個叫做<span class=\"red\">物價通脹</span>而非叫價值提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除非你蠢到連債券 股票都唔識買，咁買樓收租可能都係一個唔錯選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁bitcoin呢？呢點你就要唸未來多唔多人同你接火棒喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次講到呢到先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"樓有租金收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"但單純樓本身係無任何價值<br />\n呢個係巴菲特所指出嘅理念"},{"pid":"0f6dc3effa6ca04c0489c9680f8e433227189a93","tid":2495673,"uid":57643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b5f34514097659228230f0339a6e7ac5d8f57b84","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"30ce67fe10a0a9eab65b9c2901369fab5f6912c4","tid":2495673,"uid":329324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"278f5dd0a93e8c97d3b29fa07d72d3a367ac7f21","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"何謂投資？<br />\n巴菲特認為投資係你買一樣野，即係所謂資產<br />\n而呢樣資產可以幫到你<span class=\"red\">生產價值</span><br />\n咁先係叫投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass