kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次講到呢到先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"樓有租金收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"但單純樓本身係無任何價值<br />\n呢個係巴菲特所指出嘅理念"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"你到底明唔明佢個理念"},{"pid":"0b6c42474850dc259953bddae296523172f090cf","tid":2495673,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"黃金咁有冇價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94600d9cf302ad0bcfe0999b6f821b536d0441c8","tid":2495673,"uid":374688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"層樓可以出租賺租金，算唔算係本身會產出價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3150ba5a8d88e6532857aa0e6bc50b1ce950ce","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f6dc3effa6ca04c0489c9680f8e433227189a93","tid":2495673,"uid":57643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b5f34514097659228230f0339a6e7ac5d8f57b84","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"30ce67fe10a0a9eab65b9c2901369fab5f6912c4","tid":2495673,"uid":329324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"樓有租金收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac